283
00:19:36,759 --> 00:19:37,968
Siapa dia?

284
00:19:39,345 --> 00:19:41,847
Idola seharusnya berias
dan bertingkah lucu.

285
00:19:42,431 --> 00:19:44,600
Kenapa berkeliaran di kampus orang lain?

286
00:19:44,684 --> 00:19:47,520
Rupanya bedebah bodoh bermuka markisa!

287
00:19:48,104 --> 00:19:49,480
Tunggu. Apa?

288
00:19:50,398 --> 00:19:52,441
- "Bedebah"?
