Aku hampir kehilanganmu.

312
00:21:21,781 --> 00:21:23,491
Kupikir tak akan berlari seperti ini.

313
00:21:24,241 --> 00:21:25,534
Rupanya berguna saat kabur.

314
00:21:25,618 --> 00:21:27,161
Omong kosong. Kau selalu berlari.

315
00:21:28,871 --> 00:21:30,039
Kau tak apa-apa?

316
00:21:31,582 --> 00:21:33,751
Padahal aku hanya keluar sejenak
saat jam istirahat.

317
00:21:35,377 --> 00:21:37,046
Tolong berikan diska lepasku.

318
00:21:40,424 --> 00:21:41,550
Ini.

319
00:21:42,593 --> 00:21:46,806
Apa tugasku berhubungan
dengan kejadian tadi?

320
00:21:47,973 --> 00:21:49,767
Lari adalah cara termudah.

321
00:21:50,976 --> 00:21:52,186
Kenapa lari bersamanya?

322
00:21:53,020 --> 00:21:55,856
- Aku lari karena dia.
- Aku benci berlari.

323
00:21:56,440 --> 00:21:57,858
Kau pandai berlari.

324
00:21:58,442 --> 00:22:00,528
Baguslah kita bertemu. Kemari kau.

325
00:22:00,611 --> 00:22:04,406
Hei, aku sangat terganggu karenamu.

326
00:22:05,241 --> 00:22:07,284
Berhenti mengikutiku akunku.

327
00:22:07,368 --> 00:22:09,078
Kau pura-pura tak mendengarku?

328
00:22:09,161 --> 00:22:10,663
Hei!

329
00:22:13,874 --> 00:22:15,835
Hei!

330
00:22:17,044 --> 00:22:17,962
Hei!

