430
00:27:43,537 --> 00:27:45,289
tapi terasa jauh jika jalan kaki.

431
00:27:45,873 --> 00:27:47,165
Bagaimana denganmu?

432
00:27:47,833 --> 00:27:49,042
Kau sendirian?

433
00:27:49,585 --> 00:27:52,170
Aku bersama dengannya tadi,
tapi dia tertahan.

434
00:27:52,254 --> 00:27:53,380
Apa?

435
00:27:53,463 --> 00:27:55,424
- Tertahan siapa?
- Kau mengagetkanku.

436
00:27:56,174 --> 00:27:57,217
Entahlah.

437
00:27:57,301 --> 00:28:00,345
Dia mau ditemani sampai manajernya datang.

438
00:28:00,846 --> 00:28:03,015
Maksudku, dia merengek. Ceritanya panjang.

439
00:28:03,098 --> 00:28:04,766
Kurasa dia
sudah terbebas darinya sekarang.

440
00:28:05,767 --> 00:28:07,019
Apa tak paham maksudmu.

441
00:28:07,728 --> 00:28:09,479
